1️⃣ GROUP DISCUSSION (GD) BASICS

Many companies use GD to test:

Communication
Leadership
Listening
Confidence
Team behavior
🔹 GD STRUCTURE (How to Speak)

Use this formula:

Introduction → Point → Example → Conclusion

🎯 Sample GD Topic:

“Is Artificial Intelligence replacing human jobs?”

✅ Good Opening (30 sec)
Writing

Good morning everyone. My view is that Artificial Intelligence is transforming jobs rather than simply replacing them. While some repetitive tasks may be automated, AI is also creating new opportunities in areas like machine learning, cybersecurity, and data analysis. The key is adapting and upskilling.

🔹 GD Rules

✔ Speak first if possible (good impression)
✔ Don’t interrupt rudely
✔ Add value, don’t repeat
✔ Support with examples
✔ Summarize if given chance

2️⃣ HR TRAP QUESTIONS (VERY COMMON)
❓ Trap 1: Why should we not hire you?

Wrong ❌
“I don’t know.”

Better ✅

Writing

One area I am still improving is gaining more practical industry exposure as a fresher, but I am a fast learner and highly willing to learn on the job.

❓ Trap 2: Why should we hire you over others?

Focus on value:

Consistency
Learning attitude
Problem solving
Teamwork
❓ Trap 3: If your manager criticizes you?

Correct approach:

Writing

I would treat constructive criticism as an opportunity to improve. I would understand the feedback, correct the issue, and make sure I do better next time.

